<plot>Mabel has been living the same house for over 30 years. Widowed and stricken with emphysema she has become bitter and prejudiced. When her routine is broken by a minority courier delivering her weekly oxygen she lashes out. But when he responds with a profound gesture of kindness, Mabel begins to question the true quality of her life.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?478494</url></doc>
